code: export function nullIfEmpty(s){if(s===""||s===null||s===undefined||typeof s==="string"&&s.trim()==="")return null;return s;}export function undefinedIfEmpty(s){return nullIfEmpty(s)||undefined;}export function maybeParseInt(s){var m=undefinedIfEmpty(s);if(m!=null)return parseInt(m);else return undefined;}export function capitalise(s){if(s.length<=1)return s.toUpperCase();else return s.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+s.slice(1);}
